com.skilltradiez.skilltraderz

Class TradeList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.skilltradiez.skilltraderz.Notification
      • com.skilltradiez.skilltraderz.TradeList

  • public class TradeList
extends Notification
    We have a trade list as one of the core features within our application. Users in our application are all going to (ideally) have the goal in which case they want to trade skills with one another this list is going to be THE focus of the class/object that facilitates this entire process of trading with other users!
